Dialogue: 0,0:23:35.18,0:23:36.81,ED_JP_EP13,,0,0,0,,{\fad(240,240)\blur2}誓うのなら
Dialogue: 0,0:23:36.81,0:23:40.15,ED_JP_EP13,,0,0,0,,{\fad(240,240)\blur2}辿る空で待っていると
Dialogue: 0,0:23:40.15,0:23:41.35,ED_JP_EP13,,0,0,0,,{\fad(240,240)\blur2}I meant for you
