Dialogue: 0,0:23:57.33,0:23:59.04,ED_JP_EP13,,0,0,0,,{\fad(240,240)\blur2}We are Drifters
Dialogue: 0,0:22:33.66,0:22:39.71,ED_CH_EP13,,0,0,0,,{\fad(240,240)\blur2}去实现于天空彼方的约定吧
Dialogue: 0,0:22:41.84,0:22:47.34,ED_CH_EP13,,0,0,0,,{\fad(240,240)\blur2}我祈愿与你并肩前行
Comment: 0,0:22:47.34,0:22:49.43,ED_CH_EP13,,0,0,0,,{\fad(240,240)\blur2}Beautiful it’s beautiful
Dialogue: 0,0:22:49.84,0:22:54.14,ED_CH_EP13,,0,0,0,,{\fad(240,240)\blur2}正确与否
Dialogue: 0,0:22:54.14,0:22:56.48,ED_CH_EP13,,0,0,0,,{\fad(240,240)\blur2}只取决于自己
Dialogue: 0,0:22:57.69,0:23:04.36,ED_CH_EP13,,0,0,0,,{\fad(240,240)\blur2}时而莫衷一是
Dialogue: 0,0:23:05.24,0:23:11.28,ED_CH_EP13,,0,0,0,,{\fad(240,240)\blur2}时而词不达意
Dialogue: 0,0:23:11.28,0:23:13.33,ED_CH_EP13,,0,0,0,,{\fad(240,240)\blur2}这也无可奈何
Dialogue: 0,0:23:13.33,0:23:16.79,ED_CH_EP13,,0,0,0,,{\fad(240,240)\blur2}让弱小的我变得强大
Dialogue: 0,0:23:16.79,0:23:22.34,ED_CH_EP13,,0,0,0,,{\fad(240,240)\blur2}是为与你相称
